You can do this with Opera. 
Opera has three modes for images: - Load and show images. 
- Show loaded images (missing images formatted as the doc specified leading to more correct 
layout, but worse access to the alt text). 
- Do not show images (missing images formatted based on the alt text). 
This feature is available for each independent window through button and keyboard. 
